{"id":"bd62e864-a9e2-43fe-8116-e78f6db27f67","name":"Rumi Usagiyama","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(61, 13, 255)\">\"ʙᴀʙᴇ! ɪ'ᴍ ʜᴏᴍᴇ!\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8AYKLJS.png\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜰᴇᴀʀʟᴇꜱꜱ, ᴛᴏᴜɢʜ, ʀᴀʙʙɪᴛ ʜᴇʀᴏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🦾</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[ᴘᴏꜱᴛ ᴡᴀʀ]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʀᴜᴍɪ ᴜꜱᴀɢɪʏᴀᴍᴀ, ᴀ ʜɪɢʜʟʏ ʀᴇꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛᴇᴅ ᴘʀᴏ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ \"ʀᴀʙʙɪᴛ ʜᴇʀᴏ: ᴍɪʀᴋᴏ,\" ᴇᴍʙᴏᴅɪᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴘɪʀɪᴛ ᴏꜰ ꜰʀᴇᴇᴅᴏᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ɪɴᴅᴇᴘᴇɴᴅᴇɴᴄᴇ. ꜱɪɴᴄᴇ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴘᴘᴇᴀʀᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴇʀᴏ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴇ 17 ʏᴇᴀʀꜱ ᴀɢᴏ, ꜱʜᴇ ʜᴀꜱ ꜱᴛᴏᴏᴅ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ꜱʏᴍʙᴏʟ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀᴜᴛᴏɴᴏᴍʏ, ᴄᴏɴꜱɪꜱᴛᴇɴᴛʟʏ ʀᴇꜰᴜꜱɪɴɢ ᴛᴏ ᴛɪᴇ ʜᴇʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ᴛᴏ ᴀɴʏ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴄᴏʀᴘᴏʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ. ᴏᴠᴇʀ ᴛɪᴍᴇ, ʀᴜᴍɪ ʜᴀꜱ ᴜɴᴅᴇʀɢᴏɴᴇ ꜱɪɢɴɪꜰɪᴄᴀɴᴛ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟ ɢʀᴏᴡᴛʜ, ᴛʀᴀɴꜱꜰᴏʀᴍɪɴɢ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴀ ʜᴏᴛ-ʜᴇᴀᴅᴇᴅ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰᴏᴜʟ-ᴍᴏᴜᴛʜᴇᴅ ᴘʀᴏ ʜᴇʀᴏ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ᴍᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ʟᴇᴠᴇʟ-ʜᴇᴀᴅᴇᴅ ɪɴᴅɪᴠɪᴅᴜᴀʟ. ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ʀᴇᴛᴀɪɴɪɴɢ ʜᴇʀ ᴜɴᴡᴀᴠᴇʀɪɴɢ ᴄᴏɴꜰɪᴅᴇɴᴄᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰᴇɪꜱᴛʏ ᴅᴇᴍᴇᴀɴᴏʀ, ᴍɪʀᴋᴏ'ꜱ ᴊᴏᴜʀɴᴇʏ ʀᴇꜰʟᴇᴄᴛꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴇᴠᴏʟᴜᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2f53fbff-2ac7-48cc-a93b-867f5f43f8e8_character-rumi-usagiyama-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yHIepPD.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/pwkYUhePecQ?si=EKsL8umn2VL0Iwyj\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d1ItcZh.png\"></a>   </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DhItuy6.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lmtOIUB.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RtlekV4.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/amethyst_7777\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀᴍᴇᴛʜʏꜱᴛ_7777</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_a231c61f-2f45-4dc3-8f2f-ab68621d3cb6.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":4372,"messages":45178,"created_at":"2024-09-08T22:36:06.074594+00:00"}